                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable M</hi> 54.) I was on duty in Black<lb></lb>man-street, and heard the cry of "Stop thief"—I saw the prisoner fun<lb></lb>ning without a hat from the corner of Suffolk-street—I Saw him drop something—I pursued him about fifty or sixty yards, and stopped him and brought him back to the shop.</p>
